txt.en: Brambles should be placed around Limlók.
Trygvar, son of Runerik and Yrsa, seeks brambles to strengthen Limlók's fortifications.
Brambles can be found in the Floodfells.\n\nYou should gather brambles for Limlók.

'Aye, you must be the outsider. If father Runerik says you are welcome, then I have no trouble with you. Mother Yrsa says I should reinforce the palisades with brambles. I have gathered all the brambles to be found nearby. Would you gather the brambles found further from Limlók and apply them to the fortifications?'
